title: Potential COVID-19 symptoms reported through NHS Pathways and 111 online
description: Data published on potential COVID-19 symptoms reported through NHS Pathways and 111 online Dashboard shows the total number of NHS Pathways triages through 111 and 999, and online assessments in 111 online which have received a potential COVID-19 final disposition.
datasetNotes: On the landing page scroll to latest version and click the link, this will open a new window.  Scroll down to 'Resources' Not all spreadsheets are required. it may be possible to combine the following files into one data set:  NHS Pathways Covid-19 data 2020 and 111 Online Covid-19 Open data.  Data description (XLS) and meta data (CSV) are also available on this page
sizingNotes: Simple table structure. only 2 spreadsheets are required. it may be possible to combine the following files into one data set:  NHS Pathways Covid-19 data 2020 and 111 Online Covid-19 Open data.  Data description (XLS) and meta data (CSV) are also available on this page
